*  096 - DATATYPE returns user type name
*  Normalize DATATYPE() output to uppercase for oracle-stability across
*  engines (CSNOBOL4 uppercase, SPITBOL/snobol4x lowercase; -f/-F switches
*  also affect case fold). User field values are untouched.
        DATA('node(val,next)')
        N = node('hello', '')
        OUTPUT = REPLACE(DATATYPE(N), &LCASE, &UCASE)
        OUTPUT = val(N)
END
